  (<a href="http://www.orange.nl" title="www.orange.nl">www.orange.nl</a>)<br />
1 plan:<br />
depends on how long you call: (the longer you call the lower the cost per minute)<br />
0.17 up to 0.35 per minute and 0.09 SMS<br />
<strong>T-Mobile</strong><br />
  (<a href="http://www.t-mobile.nl" title="www.t-mobile.nl">www.t-mobile.nl</a>)<br />
a few plans<br />
from 0.10 up to 0.45 p/minute for day &amp; night difference<br />
fixed priced 0.35 p/minute and 0.23 SMS</p>
