<p>All prices are Euro, Price for SIM, depends on shop, sometimes you get fully refunded with phonecredit. Probably you will pay 5 Euro. All SIM cards are relatively easy to obtain. I don't know if it is possible to  refill with foreign credit card. If not possible, it is easy to buy refill cards. A lot shops sell them including supermarkets, and newspaper stands. Although some resellers cards are only by internet, or only in 1 brand of shop. (that is the reason why I didn't list them.</p>
